snippet.title: Botany Manor - Out Now on PS5 & PS4
snippet.description: Botany Manor blooms onto PlayStation today! Explore a historical English homestead brimming with a lifetime of memorabilia and research, uncover long-forgotten seeds and piece together clues to solve puzzles to help each rare plant grow.
